# Now here's the **important part** — you also need to fix one thing in MongoDB Atlas. Your IP `49.37.169.252/32` is added, but that IP changes every time your internet restarts. Do this right now:

# **Go to MongoDB Atlas → Network Access tab → click "ADD IP ADDRESS" → click "ALLOW ACCESS FROM ANYWHERE" → type `0.0.0.0/0` → click Confirm.**

# This makes sure the connection never breaks even if your IP changes.

